\cf0 Task:
\f1\b0  extract fingerprinting attributes/APIs and their groups from the 112 JSON files\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f2 \cf0 You are given 112 JSON files containing browser fingerprinting results. Search all files and extract every fingerprinting-related attribute/API that appears, along with its corresponding group/category if available. Use the serial prefix in each filename as the site ID. Create an Excel file with rows as sites and columns as attributes/APIs grouped under their categories. Mark each cell as FP if that attribute/API is present for that site, otherwise leave it blank. Also create a category-level sheet where each category is marked FP if any API in that category is present for that site. Keep the original site serials and do not renumber them.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa298\partightenfactor0

