\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0
\cf0 Task:
\f1\b0  search privacy-policy files for category keywords and mark declared collection
\f2 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf0 You are given privacy policy files for the same sites and a keyword list for fingerprinting-related categories. Search each privacy policy for the keywords and map the matches to the correct categories. Use the serial prefix in each filename as the site ID. Create an Excel file with rows as sites and columns as categories. Mark FP if the privacy policy indicates that data from that category will be collected, otherwise leave the cell blank. Do not renumber the sites. Keep the category names consistent across the whole file.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa298\partightenfactor0

