Prompt 3: Match Tool Excel with Policy Excel\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0
\cf0 Task:
\f1\b0  compare detected categories with declared categories\
You are given two Excel files for the same sites: one policy-declared category file and one tool-detected category file. Match them site by site and category by category using the site serial prefix. Create an Excel output where each cell is marked FP if the category is both declared in the privacy policy and detected by the tool, XX if the tool detects the category but the privacy policy does not declare it, and blank otherwise. Keep all category names and site serials exactly the same as in the input files.}